<section id="about" class="about-village-container">
  <div class="text-block">
    <p>Saving for the future is stressful. And it’s not just college. It’s sports leagues, dance classes, that first car, vacations. The list goes on. Village allows your family and friends to support these savings goals by gifting towards these experiences for your children.</p>
  </div>
